#phase2 is user traffic/IPSec SA
#crypto-map is a combination of settings for IPSec tunnels

show crypto isakmp sa #1st tunnel data
show crypto ipsec sa #2nd tunnel data
show crypto engine connections active
show crypto map

int g0/0
crypto map OUR-MAP

GUIDE IS NOT FULL!!!!

#phase1
crypto isakmp policy 10
hash md5
encryption aes 
authentication pre-share
group-2

#phase2
crypto isakmp key cisco address "out int of the 2nd site"
crypto ipsec transform-set CCNP esp-aes 128 esp-md5-hmac

#ACL
access-list VPN-HOSTS permit host 192.168.1.10 host 192.168.2.10
crypto map VPN 10 ipsec-isakmp
set peer 213.150.100.2 
set transform-set VPN 
match address VPN-HOSTS
interface g0/0/1 #out int 
crypto map VPN

done
